These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
City: liverpool, hannover
The people have 2 different jobs:  project-manager, engineer
1. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the project-manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| City   | liverpool  | hannover |
| Job     | engineer | project-manager  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, may
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, pall-mall
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Birthday    | august      | may         |
| Cigar   | bluemaster | pall-mall |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
2 different games are played: go, domino
2 different pets are kept: fish, hedgehog
1. the person playing go is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Game   | domino | go   |
| Pet       | hedgehog  | fish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-4::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  coach, dancer
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, january
1. the dancer is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| Job   | coach  | dancer |
| Birthday         | november | january    |

